---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE, url } from "../config";
---

<BaseLayout sideBarActiveItemID="home">
    <div class="pb-12 mt-5">
        <img src={url('profile.jpg')} alt="Bao Zixuan" class="w-28 h-28 mb-5 rounded-full shadow-ac object-cover" />
        <div class="text-xl py-1">Hi, I'm</div>
        <div class="text-5xl font-bold">{SITE_TITLE}</div>
        <div class="text-2xl py-2 font-bold">鲍子轩 · reverieach</div>
        <div class="text-xl py-6 leading-relaxed">
            北京邮电大学人工智能学院本科生。<br />
            我关注能真正落地的 AI 工具、桌面自动化、计算机视觉、NLP 和嵌入式智能系统。
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-10">
            <a href={url('projects')} class="btn-ac">View Projects</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/reverieach" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline rounded-ac-md">GitHub</a>
            <a href="mailto:baozixuan@bupt.edu.cn" class="btn btn-outline rounded-ac-md">Email</a>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="rounded-ac-lg bg-base-100 p-6 shadow-ac border-t-4 border-ac-primary">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">What I build</div>
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    作业提醒、游戏聊天翻译、RK3568 端侧 AI、课程实验和复习工具。项目通常从一个很具体的麻烦开始，然后做成可以每天使用的工具。
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-ac-lg bg-base-100 p-6 shadow-ac border-t-4 border-ac-green">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Site structure</div>
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    这个站点按模板保留 Projects、CV、Blog、Personal、Notes 几个入口。现在先放个人主页和项目，后续写文章只需要新增 Markdown 文件。
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-ac-lg bg-base-100 p-6 shadow-ac border-t-4 border-ac-orange">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Current focus</div>
                <ul class="list-disc ml-5 leading-8">
                    <li>AI-assisted productivity tools</li>
                    <li>Computer vision and edge inference</li>
                    <li>NLP systems and semantic matching</li>
                    <li>Small desktop apps with careful UX</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-ac-lg bg-base-100 p-6 shadow-ac border-t-4 border-ac-pink">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Now</div>
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    先把站点变成清晰可扩展的信息架构，再慢慢补 note、blog 和照片。比一页塞满所有东西更耐用。
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>
